{"tid":967220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Boxing Day我入咗廠","createTime":"2019-01-03T10:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T11:38:06.000Z","uid":109792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc5245803cf3c0029240a9707b96aa10a4ba0ef","tid":967220,"uid":109792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"本身好似係帶我細妹定貓去<br />\n好似係睇大陸醫生<br />\n話說我半夜喺屋企偷食宵夜<br />\n喺雪櫃攞左d廚師腸<br />\n入微波爐ding<br />\n仲有d芝士腸<br />\n點知比我老豆發現<br />\n然後我好驚<br />\n之後喺雪櫃攞左幾包m&amp;m<br />\n好似有d過左期 好撚難食<br />\n然後有粒好似出奇蛋<br />\n唔知點解我放左入煎pan<br />\n然後佢溶左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來再睇醫生<br />\n醫生比左個杯麵叫我食<br />\n佢scan左杯麵上面個code<br />\n然後個mon顯示左蛋白質含量<br />\n話 呢個jeng呀 好營養<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073414e93960e1f440531831bfd3191a78b9de15","tid":967220,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T10:44:17.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"67e97e45dbdcb2cd5cb8a77ef7b8f690370d53c3","tid":967220,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:38:06.000Z","msg":"去食百里香啦"}]}